## ЁЯОУ Exam / Interview Ready Answers

### Q: When should we use MVC?
A:> MVC is suitable for small to medium web applications with simple business logic.

### Q: Why Clean Architecture for banking?
A:> Because banking systems require strict separation of business rules, security, auditability, and scalability.

### Q: Can MVC and Clean Architecture be used together?
A:> Yes. MVC is used as the presentation layer inside Clean Architecture.

---

## ЁЯза One-line Memory Trick (Teaching tip)

> Blog тЖТ MVC
> Office тЖТ N-Tier
> Bank тЖТ Clean Architecture
> Amazon тЖТ Microservices





